19
00:01:55,550 --> 00:01:57,620
Won't you take a seat?

20
00:02:20,500 --> 00:02:21,610
So finally the dishes of
Gandhar did make

21
00:02:21,610 --> 00:02:24,590
their way into Hastinapur's
royal kitchen.

22
00:02:35,620 --> 00:02:37,690
It's my first try, Prince.

23
00:02:39,620 --> 00:02:40,650
I must say,
it's quite a good one.

24
00:02:47,670 --> 00:02:50,500
But it won't be famous
in Hastinapur.

25
