Till the time this thread
is tied around your wrist

129
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:11,830
you won't say a thing

130
00:10:11,850 --> 00:10:14,950
about your past to your husband.

131
00:10:18,990 --> 00:10:21,870
But... - There's no time
for options, Princess.

132
00:10:21,900 --> 00:10:24,730
A king has many wives.

133
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:27,780
If King Pandu marries
a second time

134
00:10:27,870 --> 00:10:31,900
this very secret of yours
will become a risk to your life.

135
00:10:34,810 --> 00:10:35,950
