136
00:10:36,040 --> 00:10:39,860
a secret portends
a danger to a woman.

137
00:10:46,820 --> 00:10:47,810
Why...

138
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:51,860
Why do I get the feeling

139
00:10:53,890 --> 00:10:55,930
that by tying this thread

140
00:10:57,030 --> 00:10:59,760
you have but curtailed
my breaths.

141
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:05,840
If I keep this matter
a secret from my husband

142
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:08,870
then it would be
my second crime.

143
00:11:12,010 --> 00:11:13,810
Moreover

144
00:11:17,790 --> 00:11:19,890
after having forsaken my son

145
00:11:22,820 --> 00:11:24,900
