served as his refuge.

149
00:11:46,920 --> 00:11:48,020
Would he...

150
00:11:48,950 --> 00:11:51,930
Would he have ever received
maternal love?

151
00:11:55,920 --> 00:11:57,960
Or just as an orphan

152
00:12:00,900 --> 00:12:03,880
is he destined to
suffer pangs of sorrow.

153
00:12:06,870 --> 00:12:08,850
Where could my son be?

154
