Someone, help me!

157
00:12:28,920 --> 00:12:30,960
Hey! Look! Move away!
- Help!

158
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:34,030
What's going on?
- Help!

159
00:12:35,030 --> 00:12:38,010
Run for your lives!
- Someone save him!

160
00:12:38,030 --> 00:12:40,980
Someone save him!

161
00:12:45,010 --> 00:12:47,810
Save him!

162
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:50,750
Move back!

163
00:12:50,780 --> 00:12:53,760
Move back!
- Step back! - Save him!

164
00:12:53,850 --> 00:12:55,950
What's going on!
Someone save him!

165
00:12:55,980 --> 00:12:57,760
Move!

166
00:14:16,970 --> 00:14:18,950
Son!

167
00:14:21,040 --> 00:14:23,020
Karna!

168
00:14:23,940 --> 00:14:24,960
Yes?

169
00:14:25,010 --> 00:14:27,920
Radha, your son
is indeed divine.

170
00:14:29,780 --> 00:14:31,910
Mother, I just...

171
