Mother?
Mother!

172
00:14:40,860 --> 00:14:42,840
Mother!
- Shut up, idiot!

173
00:14:42,890 --> 00:14:45,800
First you infuriate me
and then chant my name!

174
00:14:45,830 --> 00:14:47,000
Come home and I'll
take you to task!

175
00:14:48,760 --> 00:14:50,830
But why, mother?
What did I do?

176
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:52,990
I was just saving the kid.

177
00:14:53,030 --> 00:14:56,910
And what about you?
Would the Lord save you?

178
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:59,780
Why don't you think before
doing anything?

179
00:14:59,840 --> 00:15:02,820
But I don't require
any protection, mother.

180
00:15:02,810 --> 00:15:04,970
You know that already.
- Shut up and come home!

181
00:15:05,750 --> 00:15:06,980
Come on!

182
00:15:13,850 --> 00:15:15,830
Come home and I'll
take you to task!

183
00:15:16,020 --> 00:15:16,990
Come on home!

184
00:15:17,760 --> 00:15:18,860
Mother!

185
00:15:20,860 --> 00:15:22,030
Are you angry, mother?

186
00:15:22,800 --> 00:15:24,830
Son, you first infuriate me

187
00:15:24,970 --> 00:15:28,810
and then very coyly ask
if I am angry.

188
00:15:29,800 --> 00:15:32,810
Why do you do any such deed
that makes me angry?

189
00:15:32,840 --> 00:15:34,010
I'm Adhirath's son.

190
00:15:34,840 --> 00:15:36,950
I will have to save
the child, right?

191
00:15:36,940 --> 00:15:38,810
I know that.

192
00:15:38,850 --> 00:15:41,940
But I have to save you from
your father's temper, right?

193
00:15:43,020 --> 00:15:44,960
And after the deed you've
done today

194
00:15:44,990 --> 00:15:46,890
deems your punishment necessary.

195
00:15:54,960 --> 00:15:58,000
Father had gone to the Kunti
province with the King, right?

196
00:15:59,030 --> 00:16:00,930
But now he's
on his way back.

197
00:16:01,040 --> 00:16:04,950
Son, the King is coming
back with his Queen

198
00:16:05,010 --> 00:16:07,770
and we have to pay them a visit.

199
00:16:14,750 --> 00:16:16,740
Does that mean they will
actually see us?

200
00:16:16,950 --> 00:16:18,940
But why would they see us, son?

201
00:16:19,790 --> 00:16:22,830
Neither are we any criminal
nor any valorous warrior.

202
00:16:22,860 --> 00:16:24,800
Mother, haven't you
always said that

203
00:16:24,860 --> 00:16:27,840
being graced with the King's
attention is good fortune?

204
00:16:27,860 --> 00:16:29,030
Or even great misfortune.

205
00:16:29,830 --> 00:16:32,830
Son, attention from
great people

206
00:16:32,900 --> 00:16:34,770
always has a profound effect.

207
00:16:34,800 --> 00:16:37,880
Then we should be graced
with Their Highness' attention.

208
00:16:38,770 --> 00:16:39,760
But how?

209
00:16:46,780 --> 00:16:48,890
All hail!
- King Pandu!

210
00:16:49,720 --> 00:16:51,790
All hail!
- King Pandu!

211
00:16:51,950 --> 00:16:54,720
All hail!
- King Pandu!

212
